sources.title: Fallguy
sources.description: The story concerns a hot-shot teen (Ed Dugan) who stumbles onto a mob execution in progress. The gangsters conveniently set him up as the fall guy. He spends most of the picture on the run from both the cops and a brutish hit man called "the Indian" while he tries to unravel the plot against him.

sources.title: Fallguy (1962)
sources.description: Hot shot teen Sonny Martin stops to help the victim of an auto accident but quickly realizes he’s stepped into a murder in progress. Watch on RetroFlix.org:  https://retroflix.org/fallguy-1962/

sources.title: Fallguy (1962) TRASHCAN CINEMA
sources.description:
It's Friday@PizzaFLIX 
Stars: Ed Dugan, G.J. Mitchell, Louis Gartner
Director: Donn Harling

 After trying to help a victim of a car crash, a teenager finds himself enmeshed in political corruption and racketeering. Killer music score by Jaime Mendoza-Nava.

metadata.Plot: A teenager trying to help an accident victim finds himself enmeshed in political corruption and racketeering and charged with a murder he didn't commit.
metadata.Actors: Ed Dugan, G.J. Mitchell, Louis Gartner
